{"tid":610101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[92撚請入] 有冇巴打同我一樣只係對90年代有感覺?","createTime":"2018-03-29T15:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T15:47:09.000Z","uid":52429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"93b534fa0d2af4ac02971ade4b3fdc159f79b6db","tid":610101,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"記得細個嗰陣已經係英治後期<br />\n老豆喺其士集團做工程師月入$80000 (1996年) 買乜都有<br />\n電視節目仲精彩過而家<br />\n97之前香港仲係一個福地, 只要肯努力就有將來<br />\n自97之後比老懵董條仆街減人工之後老豆冇咗一大截人工消費少咗<br />\n2000年之後我睇到嘅係電視節目同埋歌影視質素不斷下降<br />\n同埋D人再冇90年代咁開心<br />\n去到2010年代可以話係一潭死水<br />\n好啦, 出黎社會做野, 份糧得$9000, 低人工高工時, 又追唔到通脹<br />\n而家嘅我已經唔會再諗將來, 因為根本冇將來, 我亦都睇唔到有將來<br />\n只係想返去90年代"},{"pid":"01916c6f39db28e7132fde80531d435056c7cca9","tid":610101,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T15:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00e21541db422c2338446b59f2ba9d0b3966af6","tid":610101,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T15:19:16.000Z","msg":"看更都皮幾啦 9000？"},{"pid":"20bb7521aad9cabdb12edc69b3a15ec101c4d2d3","tid":610101,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T15:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5da2d14c3545dd2b06e36e3723952b47589f14","tid":610101,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b00e21541db422c2338446b59f2ba9d0b3966af6","tid":610101,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T15:19:16.000Z","msg":"看更都皮幾啦 9000？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"轉咗新工"},{"pid":"1c7094fabc860c464d2f90c98bd11c20ccdb2b3e","tid":610101,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T15:20:56.000Z","msg":"咁只不過係因為你老豆食正移民潮，升左上去先揾到果個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fc4ebc57d86fde34655bcbbb7e750bdfda1